des:
Over 100 cheesy and very corny jokes. If you're in need of a laugh, or just fancy hearing some painful jokes then use this skill. Prepare for some really awful jokes, sure to make you laugh. 

- Over 100+ jokes
- Updated regularly
- Great for the whole family

Please use the following example phrases when using Cheesy Jokes:
“Alexa, please open cheesy jokes and tell me a joke”
“Alexa, launch cheesy jokes”
“Alexa, play cheesy jokes”
“Alexa, open cheesy jokes”

If you know of any other cheesy jokes, get in touch and I will add them!
https://twitter.com/VikingSkullApps
